<kml>

<concept name=Follow>
<superconcept name=Locomotion>

<hr>
<h3>Component Semantics:</h3>
<component tag=Follow>
<definition>

  to do a <conceptref name=Locomotion> with the same path as a "prior" <conceptref name=Locomotion>.

</definition>
</component>

<requiredslotlist>

  <slotdescription name=agent>
     the <conceptref name=Entity> that moves (follows).
  </slotdescription>
  <comment>
     Follow is a type of <conceptref name=Locomotion>.  Therefore, the
     <slot>agent</slot> (the <conceptref name=Entity> that causes the move) is the same
     as the <slot>object</slot> (the thing being moved).
  </comment>

  <slotdescription name=base>
     the <conceptref name=Entity> that is being followed by the <slot>agent</slot>.
  </slotdescription>

</requiredslotlist>

<examplesentencelist>

  <examplesentence>
    <text>John followed Jane to the restaurant.</text>
    <slotdescription name=agent>John</slotdescription>
    <slotdescription name=base>Jane</slotdescription>
  </examplesentence>
</examplesentencelist>

</kml>


